Class Deploy

java.lang.Object
Model.Deploy
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Orders
public class Deploy extends Object implements Orders, Serializable
Represents a Deploy order in the game, where a player deploys armies to a country.
Author:
Akhilesh Kanbarkar
